    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category</strong>: Clan</p><hr /><p><strong>Prerequisite</strong>: Hoshimi Clan</p><hr /><p>The Hoshimi clan's history is filled with poetry, each with a lesson. The one most stand out to you brings clarity both to your mind and your swordsmanship.</p><ul><li>Increase your Dexterity or Wisdom Score by +1, up to a maximum of +20.</li><li>You always know the location of your <strong>Hunt Target(s)</strong>.</li><li>You can spend 10 minutes focusing your senses. Doing this allows you to sense the nearest <strong>Abberation</strong> or <strong>Monstrosity</strong> within 1 mile of yourself. This counts as a C-Rank Sensory Jutsu for the purposes of interacting with adversary traits and jutsu.</li></ul>",
